<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Página no encontrada | Códigos de Oro</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --color-negro: #000000;
            --color-oro: #FFD700;
            --color-naranja: #FFA500;
            --color-gris-oscuro: #111111;
            --color-gris-fondo: #1a1a1a;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--color-negro);
            color: var(--color-oro);
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, var(--color-gris-oscuro) 0%, var(--color-negro) 100%);
        }

        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 10rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-oro) 0%, var(--color-naranja) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: var(--color-oro);
        }

        .error-description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.7);
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto 3rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn-home {
            background-color: var(--color-oro);
            color: var(--color-negro);
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 12px 35px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 2px solid var(--color-oro);
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: var(--color-oro);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .trophy-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--color-oro);
            opacity: 0.5;
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
        }

        .star {
            position: absolute;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            opacity: 0.3;
            animation: twinkle var(--duration) infinite;
        }

        @keyframes twinkle {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scale(1); }
            50% { opacity: 0.8; transform: scale(1.2); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Background Stars -->
    <script>
        for (let i = 0; i < 50; i++) {
            const star = document.createElement('div');
            star.className = 'star';
            const size = Math.random() * 3;
            star.style.width = size + 'px';
            star.style.height = size + 'px';
            star.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + 'vw';
            star.style.top = Math.random() * 100 + 'vh';
            star.style.setProperty('--duration', (Math.random() * 3 + 2) + 's');
            document.body.appendChild(star);
        }
    </script>

    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="trophy-icon">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="error-code">404</div>
        <h1 class="error-message">Página Extraviada</h1>
        <p class="error-description">
            Parece que el camino que buscabas no existe en nuestra gala. Quizás el enlace está roto o la página se ha retirado para los preparativos finales.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="btn-home">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i>
            Volver al inicio
        </a>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
